data.name: TEXT_ADJ_APPROVE
data.value: Continuare? Questa azione è irreversibile e comporterà l'approvazione di tutte le rettifiche che soddisfano i criteri impostati per i filtri. Se non ci sono filtri, verranno approvate tutte le rettifiche presenti nel sistema.

data.name: TEXT_ADJ_DELETE

data.name: TEXT_ADJ_DENIED

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_ITEMS_TO_AGGREGATE
data.value: (ITALIAN) For example, suppose the Decision Type is \"Use a special rate if the number of minutes of usage is over 500\". The settings might include \"500\" and the \"special rate\" to apply.

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_AGGREGATION_METHOD
data.value: (ITALIAN) Decisions are used when a monetary charge amount cannot be calculated by looking at a single record. Instead, many usage records must be examined and a total must be the number of events, units of usage, or charge amounts. The total, or aggregate, is then used to help determine the charge amount.

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_AGGREGATION_METHOD_ADD_UP_MONETARY_CHARGE
data.value: (ITALIAN) Example: \"Apply a discount if there's over $100 in charges.\"

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_AGGREGATION_METHOD_ADD_UP_UNIT_OF_USAGE
data.value: (ITALIAN) Example: \"Use a special rate if over 1,000 minutes.\"

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_AGGREGATION_METHOD_COUNT_NUMBER_OF_EVENTS
data.value: (ITALIAN) Example: \"Apply a discount if over 100 calls were made.\"

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_AGGREGATION_METHOD_FROM_PARAMETER_TABLE
data.value: (ITALIAN) Usage is aggregated based on the value set in the parameter table.

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_MULTIBUCKET
data.value: (Italian)Act on each individual record. Usage may have different prices which are determined by the bucket into which they fall.

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_SINGLEBUCKET
data.value: (Italian)Act on all the records together. All usage has same price which is determined by total volume.

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_NO_CHARGE
data.value: (Italian) Do not generate a charge for this decision
